# Flux Deal Orchestrator (Canonical Ops)

## System Boundaries (CRITICAL — Read First)
Load `config/flow-ownership.json` before ANY action.

| System | Owns | Cursor NEVER Does |
|--------|------|-------------------|
| **Comet Browser** | Lead gen, browser automation, GHL UI | Duplicate lead scraping |
| **GHL** | Customer SMS/email, trials, nurture, stage-triggered workflows | Enroll workflows via Zapier, send customer comms |
| **Website** | Stripe checkout, monthly billing | Duplicate payment links |
| **Perplexity** | Research, scoring, outreach copy | Re-score or regenerate copy |
| **Cursor** | Audit, gap-fill, stage sync, Stripe verify, Slack reports | Everything above |

## Payment & Billing
- **Stripe** = primary rail (website automations handle monthly + one-time)
- Contract ref: `FLA-YYYY-###` on Stripe metadata + GHL `fla_contract_ref`
- Square = legacy only

## GHL Stage Triggers (Automatic — Do Not Duplicate)
Stage change inside GHL fires workflows. Cursor sets stage ONLY:
- New Lead → wf_01_capture
- Qualified → wf_02_qualify
- Proposal Sent → wf_03_proposal
- Contract Signed → wf_04_onboard

**Never call `campaign`/workflow enrollment via Zapier.**

## Idempotency Tags (Check Before Every Write)
`comet_intake`, `perplexity_scored`, `ghl_wf_active`, `cursor_stage_set`, `fulfillment_complete`, `pitch_ready`

## Client Record Completeness
Load `config/client-record-schema.json`. No stage advance without required fields.

## Production Skill
Use `deal-orchestrator` (not `deal-machine`) for all production runs.

## Slack Routing
- **#war-room** (`C0BDLF5JUQ4`) — ALL deal ops: digests, audits, enrichment, pipeline status
- **#sold-clients** — contract signed + onboarding only
- **#project-update** — engineering/build updates only

## Zapier MCP Scope
Load `config/zapier-war-room.json`. Zapier focuses on **#war-room only** for deal ops.

| Zapier DOES | Zapier DOES NOT |
|-------------|-----------------|
| Post to `#war-room` | Post to `#project-update` |
| GHL idempotent upserts (gap fill, stage sync) | Enroll GHL workflows (`campaign`) |
| GHL SMS ping (internal team via tag) | Customer SMS/email |
| Stripe verify via Stripe MCP | Lead gen (Comet owns) |
| War Room alerts to Jonathan + Heaven | Browser automation |

## SMS Alerts (War Room)
Load `config/war-room-alerts.json`. Critical events SMS **Jonathan + Heaven** via **GHL only**:
- Add tag `war_room_alert_ping` to both internal GHL contacts (requires published workflow — see `docs/deal-machine/SMS-SETUP.md`)
- RingCentral is NOT used for texting
- Always post Slack `#war-room` even if GHL SMS fails
